parameters:
The heart calms down in the flickering of flames.... \! The
party's health has been fully restored!

\SE[53]So you got bitten on the arm, huh... \!\SE[12]Let's clean
up the wound for now...

\SE[23]Ah, my legs are trembling... I couldn't do anything. I
have to protect these children... \SE[52]At a time like this,
I... I can't do anything...

\SE[42] (No... That's not right! Nikita...!! \SE[57] Right now, I
don't care about reflection or regret! \SE[13] I will do what I
can for those children!!)

\SE[42] (Because Melissa is cleaning the wound for me... I will
stop the bleeding... using something as a substitute for a
bandage... \SE[13] In case of a fracture, I will use a splint...
just in case!)

\SM[nod]\SE[13]Alright, with this... It seems like there aren't
any major injuries, just some bruises... \SE[3]Just to be safe, I
want to see a doctor as soon as possible... And...

\SE[6]Panties... They got all wet, huh? \SE\SE[0]Do you want me
to lend you mine instead? \SE[0]It must be difficult with just
one hand, so should I wash your private area too?

\SE[5] (There might be scars left from the wound... But for now,
it's good... \SE[57] I absolutely have to protect these
children...)

\SE[14]It's fine, hurry!! \SE[13]I'll be okay!! Hurry, run
away!!! \SE[14]You have the role of protecting Ronoa, right!!?

The 'Forest of Escape' has been added to the teleportation
crystal!
